label: [{"start":0,"end":5,"text":"鸡衣原体病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":6,"end":10,"text":"急性暴发","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":16,"end":20,"text":"缓慢流行","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 鸡衣原体病有急性暴发的强毒力株和缓慢流行的低毒力株两大类。

label: [{"start":0,"end":1,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":9,"end":10,"text":"口","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"呼吸道","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"家禽","labels":["type"]}]
text: 鸡有较强抵抗力，经口或呼吸道感染，野鸟与家禽的接触可互相感染。

label: [{"start":4,"end":9,"text":"鸡衣原体病","labels":["disease"]},{"start":20,"end":22,"text":"火鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":37,"end":38,"text":"鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":25,"end":29,"text":"急性感染","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":32,"end":36,"text":"慢性感染","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 近年来，鸡衣原体病增多。潜伏期2～8周，火鸡和鸭为急性感染，鸽为慢性感染，鸡多为自然感染。

label: [{"start":5,"end":7,"text":"肿头","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":8,"end":12,"text":"产蛋下降","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":13,"end":17,"text":"呼吸困难","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":18,"end":25,"text":"没有产蛋高峰期","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":31,"end":37,"text":"腹部明显膨大","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":33,"end":37,"text":"明显膨大","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":45,"end":51,"text":"腹部皮肤变薄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":49,"end":51,"text":"变薄","labels":["symptom"]},{"start":6,"end":7,"text":"头","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":31,"end":33,"text":"腹部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":45,"end":49,"text":"腹部皮肤","labels":["bodypart"]}]
text: 主要症状是肿头，产蛋下降，呼吸困难，没有产蛋高峰期(70%)，腹部明显膨大，下垂伸到地面，腹部皮肤变薄。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":7,"end":9,"text":"急性","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":22,"text":"纤维素性心包炎","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":23,"end":26,"text":"肝肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":24,"end":26,"text":"肿大","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":10,"end":12,"text":"幼鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":23,"end":24,"text":"肝","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":2,"end":6,"text":"死亡率高","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 幼鸡死亡率高，急性。幼鸡剖检见纤维素性心包炎和肝肿大。

label: [{"start":0,"end":2,"text":"成鸡","labels":["type"]},{"start":2,"end":14,"text":"输卵管中有大小不等的囊泡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":7,"end":14,"text":"大小不等的囊泡","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":15,"end":21,"text":"充满清亮液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":22,"end":31,"text":"输卵管系膜增厚发白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":27,"end":31,"text":"增厚发白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":37,"end":39,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":42,"end":59,"text":"输卵管浆膜有黄色干酪样纤维蛋白渗出","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":48,"end":50,"text":"黄色","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":50,"end":57,"text":"干酪样纤维蛋白","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":60,"end":75,"text":"输卵管蛋白分泌部被大量浆液充满","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":69,"end":73,"text":"大量浆液","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":77,"end":80,"text":"囊肿样","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":81,"end":89,"text":"切开流出大量液体","labels":["pathology"]},{"start":2,"end":5,"text":"输卵管","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":22,"end":27,"text":"输卵管系膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":42,"end":47,"text":"输卵管浆膜","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":60,"end":68,"text":"输卵管蛋白分泌部","labels":["bodypart"]},{"start":35,"end":41,"text":"多量黄色硬块","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 成鸡输卵管中有大小不等的囊泡，充满清亮液体，输卵管系膜增厚发白，膜上有多量黄色硬块，输卵管浆膜有黄色干酪样纤维蛋白渗出，输卵管蛋白分泌部被大量浆液充满而呈囊肿样，切开流出大量液体。

label: [{"start":4,"end":6,"text":"疫苗","labels":["drug"]},{"start":11,"end":14,"text":"四环素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":15,"end":18,"text":"土霉素","labels":["drug"]},{"start":19,"end":23,"text":"环丙沙星","labels":["drug"]},{"start":35,"end":44,"text":"治疗与停药交替进行","labels":["control"]},{"start":48,"end":52,"text":"慢性感染","labels":["pathology"]}]
text: 防治：无疫苗。药物有：四环素、土霉素、环丙沙星，1克/千克料连用1周，治疗与停药交替进行，是消除慢性感染的有效方法。
